{"tid":1604170,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"對於《Joker》煽動暴力的說法，導演：「怎麼沒人說一次殺了 300 人的 John Wick？」","createTime":"2019-09-30T01:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T02:13:10.000Z","uid":41343,"like":156,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"ea5c7cb106edceeb66c9932a09de46b81e91d086","tid":1604170,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:27:16.000Z","msg":"DC 最新力推的獨立電影《Joker》已在金獅獎拿下最佳影片，導演 Todd Phillips 與男主角 Joaquin Phoenix 的合作已在正片上映前獲得滿堂彩，讓《Joker》獲得巨大的媒體與網路聲量。<br />\n<br />\n反之，不少影評點出的《Joker》擁有極強大煽動性的負面影響，如今 Todd Phillips 也針對此事回應，他認為大家過度針對《Joker》，為何不去譴責好萊塢電影中無數的暴力電影？甚至以《John Wick 3》為例表示這些電影就是不間斷地上演各種暴力場面，電影中的 John Wick 一次殺了 300 人，但為何觀眾都在大笑、嘶吼？這完全沒有道理。<br />\n<br />\n「這部電影是在虛構的世界中所發生的事，或許它影射了當代社會的縮影，但《Joker》是設定在 80 年代虛構世界的虛構人物。（The movie still takes place in a fictional world. It can have real-world implications, opinions, but it&rsquo;s a fictional character in a fictional world that&rsquo;s been around for 80 years）」<br />\n<br />\n近期 Warner Bros.  官方宣佈了不支持現實世界的任何槍械暴力行為的聲明，並非要將 Joker 英雄化，而是要讓大眾正視此議題。專訪中導演提及了 2012 的「Aurora 槍擊事件」，當時當地戲院正播放著 Christopher Nolan 的《The Dark Knight Rises》，不料卻發生槍手恐怖襲擊事件，有報導當時誤報兇手仿效 Joker，導致電影本身遭到誤解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2019/9/joker-violence-todd-phillips-john-wick-action-movies-dc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2019%2F9%2Fjoker-violence-todd-phillips-john-wick-action-movies-dc&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1cg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=925b42b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2019/9/joker-violence-todd-phillips-john-wick-action-movies-dc</a>"},{"pid":"538bffe53fc9ea01be64cedf4eb727cdc8f98894","tid":1604170,"uid":53515,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:30:05.000Z","msg":"Because it is too good and real"},{"pid":"06632cb5c8f496bf7d61e47336a0c3c1e1e14cc8","tid":1604170,"uid":149496,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:33:02.000Z","msg":"怪完遊戲太暴力到依家怪電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f80c9d2d693ac44e015eab06c58c17ebc847786","tid":1604170,"uid":70013,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:34:08.000Z","msg":"點解冇人怪柯南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda499c3ed19b87486cea0b9ee48c8b5b7076c6e","tid":1604170,"uid":33104,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"3f80c9d2d693ac44e015eab06c58c17ebc847786","tid":1604170,"uid":70013,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:34:08.000Z","msg":"點解冇人怪柯南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:37:45.000Z","msg":"用返美漫做比較，點解無人怪infinity war"},{"pid":"568b7964758d4d127017ce6e66dafbe65ae85543","tid":1604170,"uid":158996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:38:26.000Z","msg":"唔可以比啲狗無後果咁開槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全民魔法師] 簡易入門版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1604041\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1604041</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"072960154e579a44c148d57815c2bf62e67132f2","tid":1604170,"uid":854,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:54:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目前嚟講火魔法係最撚勁嘅野<br />\n但永遠都好似唔夠多咁<br />\n如果和理非可以幫手帶火魔法材料會唔會幫倒好撚大忙<br />\n每人跟生日日期帶其中一樣 <br />\n俾狗check袋都唔知入你乜撚野<br />\n例如1-5號帶玻璃樽（岩岩飲完未扔）<br />\n6-10號帶砂糖<br />\n11-20號白電油/汽油（入火機食煙、露營用，五金鋪買）<br />\n20-25號打火機（食煙）<br />\n26-30號帶毛巾仔<br />\n唔知齊未 見酒精都得帶出去風險好似仲低啲<br />\n不過易tk<br />\n到時收集完再傳俾前線<br />\n其他物資照舊<br />\n可以分散風險<br />\n不過唔知係咪大部分前線都會玩火魔法<br />\n前線可唔可以話俾大家聽可以點幫 帶啲咩 做咩好<br />\n<br />\n或者一人一樽漂白水/其他腐蝕性水<br />\n拿撚死垃圾防暴popo</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"48ffdcb34ba20f8a362ff8a8cd8897